    {
      "id": "39",
      "name": "推薦角色",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 42,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Tartaglia_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "達達利亞",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "達達利亞是弓箭角色中比較特別的存在，輸出手段十分依賴元素戰技。雖然弓藏的被動效果無法提高達達利亞的斷流傷害，但對於開啟元素戰技後的普通攻擊傷害提升巨大，這也讓弓藏在達達利亞武器選擇中佔據一席地位。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 15,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Yoimiya_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "宵宮",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器特化了普通攻擊輸出，而宵宮則是普通攻擊特化的角色，該武器對宵宮傷害提升的覆蓋率遠遠超過其他角色。滿精煉的弓藏對宵宮來說僅次於精一的飛雷弓，甚至高於精一的天空之翼。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 13,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/03/7998136/7f270a1c3d5be225a3c61bff4fbe4ac6_3311723060547883859.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "亞蘿伊",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器能提高",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 225, 75)"
                      ],
                      "text": "攻擊力",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "和普通攻擊傷害，而",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "亞蘿伊",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "的主要輸出方式為普通攻擊，弓藏能提供較大的傷害加成。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 38,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Fischl_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "菲謝爾",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "菲謝爾自身普通攻擊倍率不低，可以作為駐場輸出使用。弓藏的被動效果對菲謝爾提升很大，精煉一階便有40%的高額加成。同時副屬性的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 225, 75)"
                      ],
                      "text": "攻擊力百分比",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "加成也十分適合輸出角色，是駐場輸出型菲謝爾的首選四星武器。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
